{"tid":1182205,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國律師：公安立案調查後不受追訴期限制","createTime":"2019-06-02T04:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T06:23:02.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5786950ab1de26d2b4d11b0bf328e3f82d460b3a","tid":1182205,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>中國律師：公安立案調查後不受追訴期限制</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】修訂逃犯條例其中一項新的改動是，申請移交一方要保證有關罪行是在有效追訴期內。有內地律師指，內地法律根據不同罪行的最高刑罰設定追訴期，但假如公安機關已立案調查，就不受追訴期限制，無論疑犯潛逃多久，當局亦能繼續追捕及提告。<br />\n<br />\n現時中國刑法中，不同罪行有效追訴期都不同。<br />\n<br />\n最高刑期為五至十年的罪行，例如是情節嚴重的金融詐騙罪、拐賣婦女及兒童罪，有效追訴期是十年。最高刑罰為判囚十年以上的罪行，追訴期為15年。至於像殺人、綁架、搶劫、販毒等，這些最高可被判無期徒刑或死刑的罪行，追訴期為20年。假如20年後，當局仍認為必須追訴，可提請最高人民檢察院核准。<br />\n<br />\n有內地律師指出，假如是當局已立案調查的案件則不受追訴期限制，隨時可抓捕或申請引渡疑犯。<br />\n<br />\n假如疑犯涉及多宗案件，追訴期亦會一直延長，由最後犯罪的日子計算，追究以往罪行的刑責。<br />\n<br />\n內地律師張起淮又指，即使是同一項罪名，法官都可根據案情嚴重性作不同判刑，但在內地刑法中早已列明各項罪行的最高刑罰，因此在界定追訴期時不存在不清晰的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=350166&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350166%26refer%3DShare&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIxVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=5bff4bfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350166%26refer%3DShare&h=ccd0afee\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=350166&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"18d0fbe44c8ca77a27b09b0da02489f40b0acea6","tid":1182205,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"李家超真係昆人唔使本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4161718e331ca5f7e4043a9f8d57f2b8ec19e5","tid":1182205,"uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T05:56:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">內地律師張起淮又指，即使是同一項罪名，法官都可根據案情嚴重性作不同判刑，但在內地刑法中早已列明各項罪行的最高刑罰</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd14861bb68f23c86738f5d0f043199246ed41f9","tid":1182205,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:06:09.000Z","msg":"雖遠必誅變成雖久必誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f72d34e74e250c2cf6995d2cf363a83f2e2b59","tid":1182205,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:08:13.000Z","msg":"幫香港市民全部立個案先"},{"pid":"3b187f43b504bca27bb07314193ef9f11b6f7db5","tid":1182205,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d739f4c637c5562967bc9f624dd2ef772a2262","tid":1182205,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c89a914079448c47faf57acae0aef660d6edeb5","tid":1182205,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"林鄭李家超張建宗仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}